nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/call-of-duty-modern-warfare-3-diablo-4-game-pass-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/call-of-duty-modern-warfare-3-diablo-4-game-pass-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/call-of-duty-modern-warfare-3-diablo-4-game-pass-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/call-of-duty-modern-warfare-3-diablo-4-game-pass-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/call-of-duty-modern-warfare-3-diablo-4-game-pass-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/activision-blizzard">动视暴雪</a>宣布<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/call-of-duty-modern-warfare-3"><em>，《使命召唤：现代战争 3》</em></a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/diablo-4"><em>《暗黑破坏神 4》</em></a>今年都不会包含在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/pc">PC</a>或<a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/xbox-game-pass">Xbox Game Pass</a>中。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/game-reviews/diablo-4-review-3446891">《暗黑破坏神 4》评论：死灵法师日记</a></strong></li></ul><p>“随着我们继续努力争取监管机构批准<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/microsoft">微软</a>交易，我们一直收到一些疑问，我们即将推出和最近推出的游戏是否可以通过 Game Pass 获得，”它<a href="https://twitter.com/ATVI_AB/status/1711464921077006751" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在 X (FKA Twitter) 上发的帖子中</a>表示。</p><p> “虽然我们今年没有计划将<em>《现代战争 3》</em>或<em>《暗黑破坏神 4》</em>纳入 Game Pass，但一旦交易完成，我们预计将开始与<a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/xbox">Xbox</a>合作，将我们的游戏带给世界各地的更多玩家。 </p><figure id="attachment_3485135" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3485135" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="wp-image-3485135 size-full" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/modern-warfare-3-major-character-deaths.jpg" alt="《使命召唤：现代战争 3》中的普莱斯队长 图片来源：动视" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/modern-warfare-3-major-character-deaths.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/modern-warfare-3-major-character-deaths-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/modern-warfare-3-major-character-deaths-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/modern-warfare-3-major-character-deaths-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/modern-warfare-3-major-character-deaths-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/modern-warfare-3-major-character-deaths-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3485135" class="wp-caption-text"> 《使命召唤：现代战争 3》图片来源：动视</figcaption></figure><p>“我们预计我们将在明年的某个时候开始将游戏添加到 Game Pass 中，”它总结道。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/microsoft">微软</a>收购动视暴雪的最新进展报告显示，英国竞争与市场管理局（CMA）已<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/microsoft-gets-one-step-closer-to-buying-call-of-duty-developer-activision-blizzard-3502676">暂时批准</a>此项收购。</p><p>由于存在“残余担忧”，监管机构无法全面批准，但微软<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/microsoft-will-finish-buying-activision-blizzard-next-week-claims-report-3510757">显然希望在未来几天内发布积极的公告</a>。</p><p> CMA 一直是动视暴雪和微软收购之路上最大的障碍之一。微软继续拒绝收购条款，导致<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/call-of-duty-could-come-to-ubisoft-in-new-activision-microsoft-agreement-3486426">微软向育碧永久提供当前和新的动视暴雪 PC 和游戏机游戏的流媒体播放权</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3419713" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3419713" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3419713" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Diablo-4-open-beta-servers.jpg" alt="《暗黑破坏神 4》。图片来源：暴雪娱乐。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Diablo-4-open-beta-servers.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Diablo-4-open-beta-servers-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Diablo-4-open-beta-servers-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Diablo-4-open-beta-servers-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Diablo-4-open-beta-servers-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Diablo-4-open-beta-servers-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3419713" class="wp-caption-text"> 《暗黑破坏神 4》图片来源：暴雪娱乐</figcaption></figure><p>微软解释说：“根据重组交易，微软将无法在自己的云流媒体服务 Xbox Cloud Gaming 上独家发布动视暴雪游戏，也无法独家控制竞争对手服务的动视暴雪游戏的许可条款。”</p><p>因此，在交易完成之前，尚不清楚这将如何影响动视暴雪将<em>《使命召唤：现代战争 3》</em>和<em>《暗黑破坏神 4》</em>添加到 Xbox Game Pass 的计划的及时性。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/the-last-of-us-part-ii"><em>《最后生还者第二部》</em></a>出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/playstation-plus">PlayStation Plus</a>的宣传材料中，表明<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-last-of-us-part-2-may-be-coming-to-playstation-plus-3511852">该游戏可能很快就会推出订阅服务</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/call-of-duty-modern-warfare-3-and-diablo-4-wont-be-coming-to-game-pass-this-year-3512288">《使命召唤：现代战争 3》和《暗黑破坏神 4》今年不会出现在 Game Pass 上的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
